.TH btctax-reconcile-import-selections 1  btctax "btctax manual"
.SH NAME
import\-selections \- §A.4 Batch import LotSelections from a CSV (disposal_ref,origin_event_id,split_sequence,sat)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBimport\-selections\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fICSV\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
§A.4 Batch import LotSelections from a CSV (disposal_ref,origin_event_id,split_sequence,sat)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
<\fICSV\fR>
CSV of lot picks imported as LotSelection decisions (§A.4). The header is REQUIRED and
validated loudly; rows sharing a disposal_ref are grouped into a single decision.
disposal_ref is the disposal event\*(Aqs ref (disposals.csv `event` column); origin_event_id
is the lot\*(Aqs origin (lots.csv `origin_event` column).

FORMAT (header + one sample row):
  disposal_ref,origin_event_id,split_sequence,sat
  import|gemini|trade|T\-2.O\-2,import|coinbase|X,0,1000000
